General Assembly Senate Joint
Resolution No. 10
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 1223
Referred to Committee on EXECUTIVE AND LEGISLATIVE
NOMINATIONS
Introduced by:
SEN. DUFF, 25th Dist.
REP. CONCEPCION, 4th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF DR. ANDREW
CARLSON OF MILFORD TO BE A MEMBER OF THE STATE BOARD
OF EDUCATION.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Dr. Andrew
2 Carlson of Milford to be appointed a member of the State Board of
3 Education, in succession to Juan C. Salazar, to serve a term ending
4 February 28, 2028, or until a successor is appointed and has qualified,
5 whichever is longer, is hereby approved and confirmed.
LCO No. 1223 1 of 1

